-- Ukraine to Sell State Coal Mines From Next Year, Kommersant Says
-- B y   K a t e r y n a   C h o u r s i n a
-- 2012-06-25T08:26:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-25/ukraine-to-sell-state-coal-mines-from-next-year-kommersant-says.html
Ukraine will seek to sell coal mines
with the largest deposits next year,  Kommersant-Ukraine 
reported, citing Oleksandr Ryabchenko, head of the  State
Property Fund .  Bidders will compete by offering investment plans for the
mines, Ryabchenko said, according to the Kiev-based newspaper.
